Class Monomer

java.lang.Object
org.openscience.cdk.ChemObject
org.openscience.cdk.AtomContainer
org.openscience.cdk.Monomer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, IAtomContainer, ICDKObject, IChemObject, IChemObjectListener, IMonomer
Direct Known Subclasses:
AminoAcid, DebugMonomer, PDBMonomer
public class Monomer extends AtomContainer implements Serializable, IMonomer, Cloneable
A Monomer is an AtomContainer which stores additional monomer specific informations for a group of Atoms.
